Package: friendlyShiny
Title: User-friendly interface to shiny to create interactive code
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: "Chris Hammill <cfhammill@gmail.com> [aut, cre]"
Description: A (hopefully) user friendly interface to shiny's core interactivity functionality, provides
a recognizable syntax for specifying reactive elements in code chunk without the overhead of designing
the user interface and coding the applet by hand. 
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
License: GPL
LazyData: true
